<!DOCTYPE html>   
<html>   
<head>   
<meta charset="UTF-8">   
<title>Domain1上的发送者页面sender.html</title>   
<script>
function sendInfoToAnotherDomain(){   
           
    console.log("entering method: sendInfoToAnotherDomain()");   
          
var sendData={
            "name":"deals_list",
            "event":"deals_click",
            "e_data":"这是发送的数据"
        }           
           
    var iframe=window.frames[0];       
    iframe.postMessage(sendData,"*");   
             
}  
</script>   
</head>   
<body>   
       
<p>这个页面是HTML5跨域访问的Domain1上的页面sender.html，它将发送一些信息到Domain2上的receiver.html</p>   
<input type="button" value="点击则发送事件到Domain2" onclick="sendInfoToAnotherDomain();"/>   <iframe width="1200" src="receiver.html"></iframe> 
</body>   
</html>  
